“The coupé is in Maserati’s DNA.”
The insinuating curves of the #MaseratiGranTurismo prepare you for the spine-tingling sensation you get behind its wheel.

#Maserati

node.text: “A lot of my success has evolved from working hard. I was never the fastest, biggest, strongest. But I was always out in the yard, in the weight room. There was something about my will, my spirit, my passion that I knew I was going to be a special player.” - @juice_landry. Whether on the field in a helmet, or everyday life, Jarvis Landry is Powered by Passion to reach his max performance. The same principle that makes the #MaseratiLevanteTrofeo the ultimate dynamic SUV. #Maserati

node.text: You might know @juice_landry as the wide receiver on the @clevelandbrowns. But do you know Jarvis the poet? That’s the Jarvis that’s rarely seen — a man who can color outside the lines, making him a one-of-a-kind NFL player and a perfect match for the Levante. Head to our Stories to get to know the man that’s Unique by Design, in the car that audaciously follows that same principle. #Maserati

node.text: Go the distance in true #Maserati style. The new MC20 strikes the perfect balance between true craftsmanship and unparalleled engineering.

node.text: Lightning fast and feather-light —the new #MaseratiMC20 reaches 0-60 mph in just 2.9 seconds making it the fastest on-road #Maserati ever. ⚡️Visit the link in bio to learn more about The First of its Kind.

node.text: Every inch of the new MC20 is crafted for a one-of-a-kind experience that’s distinctly #Maserati. With a heart of a Nettuno engine and top speed of 202 mph, the new MC20 is here and ready to conquer. Hit the link in bio to learn more.

node.text:
What’s faster: a #Maserati Quattroporte Trofeo or a recurve bow arrow? At 203 mph, the Quattroporte Trofeo is the fastest executive sedan in the world.* The arrow? 150 mph top speed.

*Based on top speed. Class based on Maserati Premium Full Size Large Car segment.
